Subject: nvme-pci: add the DISABLE_WRITE_ZEROES quirk for a Samsung PM1725a

From: Dmitry Monakhov <dmtrmonakhov@yandex-team.ru>

[ Upstream commit abbb5f5929ec6c52574c430c5475c158a65c2a8c ]

